org.hps.record.triggerbank

Class VTPPairsTrigger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.triggerbank.VTPPairsTrigger

  • public class VTPPairsTrigger
extends Object
    Class VTPPairsTrigger Parse HPS Pairs Trigger of VTP and store information. HPS Pairs Trigger:
    • 10bit [0 : 9] trigger time in 4 ns unit
    • 4bit [10 : 13] pass bits
    • 3bit [19 : 22] pair cluster trigger bit instance: 0 to 3
